{
  "chapter": 49,
  "chapter_summary": "林仙儿在阿飞睡着后独自服食珍珠粉，随后乘轿前往僻静郊外密会四名手下。黑衣人汇报宝庆收账完毕，但追踪说书孙老头祖孙失败；圆脸中年人上缴银票利润却逐年递减，林仙儿表面温言安抚后暗中命蓝衣少年将其诛杀。灰衣人汇报龙啸云已回兴云庄，同行有胡不归和吕姓双戟客，并推测卖酒驼子与孙老头有关，疑为昔年\"背上一座山\"的孙老二。林仙儿分别对灰衣人和黑衣人低声布置任务。荆无命突然现身树林，以雷霆剑法杀死灰衣人和黑衣人，蓝衣少年目睹其快剑心生惧意，但在林仙儿的激将下仍挺剑迎战。荆无命认出其点苍派剑法，提及谢天灵和已死于自己剑下的郭嵩阳，悬念丛生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我不是不信，只不过……我应该养你的，我不能让你受苦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我知道你是真心对我好，从来也没有人对我这么好，可是，我们两人既然已这么好了，你就不该再分什么你的，我的……连我的心都已是你的了，你难道不知道？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿飞若知道这瓶珍珠粉值多少钱，一定会吓一跳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天已经是十月初五了吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四位远来辛苦了，这里也没有备酒替四位洗尘接风，真是抱歉得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道四位都有些话要说，但谁先说呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "姑娘过奖了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "我求你做的两样事，想必定是马到成功，我知道你从未令我失望的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "宝庆那一带的账都已完全收齐了，这里一共是九千八百五十两，开的是山西同福号的银票。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "这次辛苦你了，我真不知道该怎么感谢你才好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "谢字不敢当，只要姑娘还记得我这人也就是了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "但那说书的孙老头和他那孙女呢？你想必已追查出了他们的下落吧。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我本来一直跟着他们的，但到了关中道上，这两人就忽然失踪了，关中道上的朋友谁也没有看到过这么样的两个人，这两人就像……就像忽然从地上消失了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这两人的行踪实在太神秘，表面上虽装做不会武功，但我绝不相信，只要姑娘再给我些日子，我一定能追出他们的来历。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "不必了，我也知道你一定跟不住他们的，这件事你虽未做成，我也不怪你，等会儿我还有要求你帮忙的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "兄台先请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "做生意讲究的就是和气生财，你现在真不愧是个大老板的样子。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我只不过是姑娘手下的一个小伙计而已，姑娘若不赏饭吃，我就得卷铺盖，大老板这三字，我是万万不敢当的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "说什么老板，讲什么伙计，我的生意就是你的生意，只要好好地去做，这生意总有一天是你的。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "多谢姑娘，多谢姑娘……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这里是去年一年赚的纯利，也开的是同福号的银票，请姑娘过目。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "真辛苦你了，我早就知道你不但老实可靠，而且人又能干……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "怎么只有六千两？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是六千三百两。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "去年呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "九千四百两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "前年呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "前年好像……好像有一万多。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "你本事可真不小，居然把买卖越做越回去了，照这样再做两年，咱们岂非就要贴老本了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "这两年不兴缎子衣服，府绸的赚头也不大，等到明年春天的时候，就一定会有转机了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "这两年来，我知道你很辛苦，也该回家去享几年清福了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "可是……可是那边的生意……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "text": "那边的生意我自然会找人去接，你也不用操心。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_yuan_yuan_de_zhong_nian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "脸圆圆的中年人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "姑娘莫非……莫非要……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "好剑法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "text": "龙啸云已回了兴云庄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "已回去快半个月了，和他同行的除了胡不归胡疯子之外，还有个姓吕的，据说是'温侯银戟'吕凤先的堂弟，用的也是双戟，看样子武功也不弱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "text": "那卖酒的驼子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "还在那里卖酒，这人倒真是深藏不露，谁也猜不透他的来历，龙啸云已到他那小店里去了两三次，看样子也还是一点结果都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "text": "但我知道你……你必定已打听出一点来了，无论那人是什么变的，要瞒过你这双眼睛却困难得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "若是我猜得不错，那驼子必定和说书的孙老头有些关系，说不定就是昔年那'背上一座山，山也压不倒'的孙老二。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "text": "你再去打听打听，明天……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我知道……我记得……我先去了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你过来，我有话告诉你，后天晚上……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是，是，是，我明白，我怎会忘记？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣少年",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "林姑娘你倒真是忙得很。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lan_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "有什么法子呢？他们可不像你跟我……我总得敷衍敷衍他们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lan_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你生气了么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衣少年",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_lan_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "你瞧你，就像个孩子似的，快上轿子，我替你消气。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你手里这把刀能杀得死人么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "自然能杀得死人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "好，来杀我吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我与你无冤无仇，为何要杀你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 49,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "因为你不杀我，我也要杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
